<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="taxonomic history">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Taxonomic history.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Originally described as a genus by 
<bibRefCitation author="Sharp, D" journalOrPublisher="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="53 - 80" publicationUrl="https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/577106" refId="B258" refString="Sharp, D, 1882. Fam. Hydrophilidae. Biologia Centrali-Americana Insecta. Coleoptera 1 (2): 53 - 80, https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/577106" title="Fam. Hydrophilidae. Biologia Centrali-Americana Insecta." url="https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/577106" volume="1" year="1882">Sharp (1882)</bibRefCitation>
